data.description: VA Assumable loan at 2.99%. This delightful property boasts a welcoming Designer Style interior  The great room adds to the spacious feel, while the kitchen is a chef's dream with two toned cabinets, SS appliances, a pantry, granite counters, and a center island that includes a breakfast bar. The main bedroom offers privacy with an attached bathroom and walk-in closet. Outside, the covered patio overlooks scenic mountain views and a yard with artificial turf, providing enough space for play or festive barbecues. Corner lot in an amazing community. Built in tempature controled office is located in the Garage for added work at home space. Seller to contribute to closing costs to help buy down the interest rate.
